210  private static bool TryGetGrid(MyEntity entity, out MyCubeGrid grid)

280  private static List<DroneTarget> DroneProcessTargets(List<MyEntity> targets)
281  {
282  List<DroneTarget> targetPairs = new List<DroneTarget>();
283  if (targets != null)
284  {
285  foreach (MyEntity t in targets)
286  {
287  if (t is MyCubeGrid)
288  {
289  foreach (var block in ((MyCubeGrid)t).GetBlocks())
290  {
291  if (block.FatBlock is MyShipController)
292  targetPairs.Add(new DroneTarget((MyEntity)block.FatBlock, 8));
293 
294  if (block.FatBlock is MyReactor)
295  targetPairs.Add(new DroneTarget((MyEntity)block.FatBlock, 6));
296 
297  if (block.FatBlock is MyUserControllableGun)
298  targetPairs.Add(new DroneTarget((MyEntity)block.FatBlock, 10));
299  }
300  }
301  else
302  {
303  targetPairs.Add(new DroneTarget(t));
304  }
305  }
306  }
307  return targetPairs;
308  }

310  private static MyRemoteControl DroneGetRemote(string entityName)
311  {
312  var entity = GetEntityByName(entityName);
313  if (entity == null)
314  {
315  Debug.Fail("Entity of name \"" + entityName + "\" was not found.");
316  return null;
317  }
318 
319  MyRemoteControl remote = entity as MyRemoteControl;
320  if (entity is MyCubeBlock && remote == null)
321  entity = ((MyCubeBlock)entity).CubeGrid;
322 
323  if (entity is MyCubeGrid)
324  {
325  foreach (var block in ((MyCubeGrid)entity).GetBlocks())
326  {
327  if (block.FatBlock is MyRemoteControl)
328  {
329  remote = block.FatBlock as MyRemoteControl;
330  break;
331  }
332  }
333  }
334  Debug.Assert(remote != null, "Remote control was not found.");
335  return remote;
336  }

338  private static void SetDroneBehaviourMethod(string entityName, string presetName, List<MyEntity> waypoints, List<DroneTarget> targets,
339  bool activate, bool assignToPirates, int playerPriority, TargetPrioritization prioritizationStyle, float maxPlayerDistance, bool cycleWaypoints)
340  {
341  MyRemoteControl remote = DroneGetRemote(entityName);
342  if (remote != null)
343  {
344  if (waypoints != null)
345  {
346  // Remove all null waypoints -- bad input protection.
347  for (var index = 0; index < waypoints.Count;)
348  {
349  if (waypoints[index] == null)
350  {
351  waypoints.RemoveAtFast(index);
352  }
353  else
354  {
355  index++;
356  }
357  }
358  }
359 
360  var blocks = remote.CubeGrid.GetBlocks();
361  if (assignToPirates)
362  remote.CubeGrid.ChangeGridOwnership(GetPirateId(), MyOwnershipShareModeEnum.Faction);
363  MyDroneStrafeBehaviour behaviourComponent = new MyDroneStrafeBehaviour(remote, presetName, activate, waypoints, targets, playerPriority, prioritizationStyle, maxPlayerDistance, cycleWaypoints);
364  remote.SetAutomaticBehaviour(behaviourComponent);
365  if (activate)
366  remote.SetAutoPilotEnabled(true);
367  }
368  }

661  public static void MusicPlayMusicCue(string cueName, bool playAtLeastOnce = true)
662  {
663  if (MyAudio.Static == null)
664  return;
665  if (MyMusicController.Static == null)
666  {
667  MyMusicController.Static = new MyMusicController(MyAudio.Static.GetAllMusicCues());
668  MyAudio.Static.MusicAllowed = false;
669  MyMusicController.Static.Active = true;
670  }
671  MyCueId cue = MyAudio.Static.GetCueId(cueName);
672  if (!cue.IsNull)
673  {
674  MySoundData soundData = MyAudio.Static.GetCue(cue);
675  if (soundData.Category.Equals(MUSIC))
676  {
677  MyMusicController.Static.PlaySpecificMusicTrack(cue, playAtLeastOnce);
678  }
679  else
680  {
681  Debug.Fail("Cue of name \"" + cueName + "\" is not music.");
682  }
683  }
684  else
685  {
686  Debug.Fail("Cue of name \"" + cueName + "\" was not found.");

1514  public static void CreateExplosion(Vector3D position, float radius, int damage = 5000)
1515  {

1517  if (radius < 2)
1518  explosionType = MyExplosionTypeEnum.WARHEAD_EXPLOSION_02;
1519  else if (radius < 15)
1520  explosionType = MyExplosionTypeEnum.WARHEAD_EXPLOSION_15;
1521  else if (radius < 30)
1522  explosionType = MyExplosionTypeEnum.WARHEAD_EXPLOSION_30;
1523 
1524  // Create explosion
1525  MyExplosionInfo info = new MyExplosionInfo
1526  {
1527  PlayerDamage = 0,
1528  Damage = damage,
1529  ExplosionType = explosionType,
1530  ExplosionSphere = new BoundingSphereD(position, radius),
1531  LifespanMiliseconds = MyExplosionsConstants.EXPLOSION_LIFESPAN,
1532  CascadeLevel = 0,
1533  ParticleScale = 1,
1534  Direction = Vector3.Down,
1535  VoxelExplosionCenter = position,
1536  ExplosionFlags = MyExplosionFlags.AFFECT_VOXELS |
1537  MyExplosionFlags.APPLY_FORCE_AND_DAMAGE |
1538  MyExplosionFlags.CREATE_DEBRIS |
1539  MyExplosionFlags.CREATE_DECALS |
1540  MyExplosionFlags.CREATE_PARTICLE_EFFECT |
1541  MyExplosionFlags.CREATE_SHRAPNELS |
1542  MyExplosionFlags.APPLY_DEFORMATION,
1543  VoxelCutoutScale = 1.0f,
1544  PlaySound = true,
1545  ApplyForceAndDamage = true,
1546  ObjectsRemoveDelayInMiliseconds = 40
1547  };
1548  MyExplosions.AddExplosion(ref info);

1792  [VisualScriptingMiscData("Entity")]
1793  [VisualScriptingMember(true)]
1794  public static bool ChangeOwner(string entityName, long playerId = 0, bool factionShare = false, bool allShare = false)
1795  {
1796  var sharingOption = MyOwnershipShareModeEnum.None;
1797  if(factionShare)
1798  sharingOption = MyOwnershipShareModeEnum.Faction;
1799  if(allShare)
1800  sharingOption = MyOwnershipShareModeEnum.All;
1801 
1802  MyEntity entity;
1803  if (MyEntities.TryGetEntityByName(entityName, out entity))
1804  {
1805  var block = entity as MyCubeBlock;
1806  if (block != null)
1807  {
1808  // Has to use the intermediate "No Ownership" value
1809  block.ChangeBlockOwnerRequest(0, sharingOption);
1810  if (playerId > 0)
1811  block.ChangeBlockOwnerRequest(playerId, sharingOption);
1812  return true;
1813  }
1814 
1815  var grid = entity as MyCubeGrid;
1816  if (grid != null)
1817  {
1818  foreach (var fatBlock in grid.GetFatBlocks())
1819  {
1820  if(!(fatBlock is MyLightingBlock) && (fatBlock is MyFunctionalBlock || fatBlock is MyShipController))
1821  {
1822  // Has to use the intermediate "No Ownership" value
1823  fatBlock.ChangeBlockOwnerRequest(0, sharingOption);
1824  if (playerId > 0)
1825  fatBlock.ChangeBlockOwnerRequest(playerId, sharingOption);
1826  }
1827  }
1828 
1829  return true;
1830  }
1831  }
1832 
1833  return false;
1834  }

2389  // Common logic used for highlighting objects from logic provider
2390  private static void SetHighlight(MyHighlightSystem.MyHighlightData highlightData, long playerId)
2391  {
2392  var highlightComp = MySession.Static.GetComponent<MyHighlightSystem>();
2393  // Determine if we are getting rid of the highlight or updating/adding it
2394  var enabled = highlightData.Thickness > -1;
2395  // Try to find exclusive key in the local dictionary
2396  var exclusiveKey = -1;
2397  if (m_playerIdsToHighlightData.ContainsKey(playerId))
2398  {
2399  exclusiveKey = m_playerIdsToHighlightData[playerId].Find(tuple => tuple.Item1 == highlightData.EntityId).Item2;
2400  // Tuples default int value is 0 and keys are in range of 10+
2401  if (exclusiveKey == 0)
2402  exclusiveKey = -1;
2403  }
2404 
2405  // Add requst data with empty exclusive key for non existent records
2406  if (exclusiveKey == -1)
2407  {
2408  // We have nothing to disable highlight for
2409  if (!enabled)
2410  return;
2411  // Listen to accepted and rejected events - They are being unregistered afterwards
2412  highlightComp.ExclusiveHighlightAccepted += OnExclusiveHighlightAccepted;
2413  highlightComp.ExclusiveHighlightRejected += OnExclusiveHighlightRejected;
2414 
2415  if (!m_playerIdsToHighlightData.ContainsKey(playerId))
2416  m_playerIdsToHighlightData.Add(playerId, new List<MyTuple<long, int>>());
2417 
2418  m_playerIdsToHighlightData[playerId].Add(new MyTuple<long, int>(highlightData.EntityId, -1));
2419  }
2420  else if (!enabled)
2421  {
2422  // Removing the highlight
2423  // Remove the data from per player repository
2424  m_playerIdsToHighlightData[playerId].RemoveAll(tuple => tuple.Item2 == exclusiveKey);
2425  }
2426 
2427  // Do the request
2428  highlightComp.RequestHighlightChangeExclusive(highlightData, exclusiveKey);
2429  }
2430 
2431  private static void OnExclusiveHighlightRejected(MyHighlightSystem.MyHighlightData data, int exclusiveKey)
2432  {
2433  m_playerIdsToHighlightData[data.PlayerId].RemoveAll(tuple => tuple.Item1 == data.EntityId);
2434  // unsubscribe the second event
2435  MySession.Static.GetComponent<MyHighlightSystem>().ExclusiveHighlightAccepted -= OnExclusiveHighlightAccepted;
2436  }
2437 
2438  private static void OnExclusiveHighlightAccepted(MyHighlightSystem.MyHighlightData data, int exclusiveKey)
2439  {
2440  // Already disposed data
2441  if (data.Thickness == -1f)
2442  return;
2443 
2444  var playersList = m_playerIdsToHighlightData[data.PlayerId];
2445  var indexOf = playersList.FindIndex(tuple => tuple.Item1 == data.EntityId);
2446  var originalData = playersList[indexOf];
2447  m_playerIdsToHighlightData[data.PlayerId][indexOf] = new MyTuple<long, int>(originalData.Item1, exclusiveKey);
2448  // unsubscribe the second event
2449  MySession.Static.GetComponent<MyHighlightSystem>().ExclusiveHighlightRejected -= OnExclusiveHighlightRejected;
2450  }

3394  MyGuiControlBase currentControl = control.Controls.GetControlByName(splits[0]);
3395  for (int index = 1; index < splits.Length; index++)
3396  {
3397  var controlParent = currentControl as MyGuiControlParent;
3398  if (controlParent != null)
3399  {
3400  currentControl = controlParent.Controls.GetControlByName(splits[index]);
3401  continue;
3402  }
3403  var scrollPanel = currentControl as MyGuiControlScrollablePanel;
3404  if (scrollPanel != null)
3405  {
3406  currentControl = scrollPanel.Controls.GetControlByName(splits[index]);
3407  continue;
3408  }
3409  if (currentControl != null)
3410  {
3411  currentControl = currentControl.Elements.GetControlByName(splits[index]);
3412  }
3413 
3414  break;
3415  }
3416 
3417  return currentControl;
3418  }

4327  private static void SpawnAlignedToGravityWithOffset(string name, Vector3D position, Vector3D direction, string newGridName, long ownerId = 0, float gravityOffset = 0, float gravityRotation = 0)
4328  {
4329  var localBPPath = Path.Combine(MyFileSystem.UserDataPath, "Blueprints", "local");
4330  var localBPFullPath = Path.Combine(localBPPath, name, "bp.sbc");
4331  MyObjectBuilder_ShipBlueprintDefinition[] blueprints = null;
4332 
4333  if (MyFileSystem.FileExists(localBPFullPath))
4334  {
4335  MyObjectBuilder_Definitions definitions;
4336  if(!MyObjectBuilderSerializer.DeserializeXML(localBPFullPath, out definitions))
4337  {
4338  Debug.Fail("Blueprint of name: " + name + " was not found.");
4339  return;
4340  }
4341 
4342  blueprints = definitions.ShipBlueprints;
4343  }
4344 
4345  if (blueprints == null)
4346  return;
4347 
4348  // Calculate transformations
4349  Vector3 gravity = MyGravityProviderSystem.CalculateNaturalGravityInPoint(position);
4350 
4351  // Get artificial gravity
4352  if(gravity == Vector3.Zero)
4353  gravity = MyGravityProviderSystem.CalculateArtificialGravityInPoint(position);
4354 
4355  Vector3D up;
4356 
4357  if (gravity != Vector3.Zero)
4358  {
4359  gravity.Normalize();
4360  up = -gravity;
4361  position = position + gravity * gravityOffset;
4362  if(direction == Vector3D.Zero)
4363  {
4364  direction = Vector3D.CalculatePerpendicularVector(gravity);
4365  if(gravityRotation != 0)
4366  {
4367  var rotationAlongAxis = MatrixD.CreateFromAxisAngle(up, gravityRotation);
4368  direction = Vector3D.Transform(direction, rotationAlongAxis);
4369  }
4370  }
4371  }
4372  else
4373  {
4374  if(direction == Vector3D.Zero)
4375  {
4376  direction = Vector3D.Right;
4377  up = Vector3D.Up;
4378  } else
4379  {
4380  up = Vector3D.CalculatePerpendicularVector(-direction);
4381  }
4382  }
4383 
4384  List<MyObjectBuilder_CubeGrid> cubeGrids = new List<MyObjectBuilder_CubeGrid>();
4385  foreach (var blueprintDefinition in blueprints)
4386  {
4387  foreach (var cubeGrid in blueprintDefinition.CubeGrids)
4388  {
4389  cubeGrid.CreatePhysics = true;
4390  cubeGrid.EnableSmallToLargeConnections = true;
4391  cubeGrid.PositionAndOrientation = new MyPositionAndOrientation(position, direction, up);
4392  cubeGrid.PositionAndOrientation.Value.Orientation.Normalize();
4393 
4394  if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(newGridName))
4395  cubeGrid.Name = newGridName;
4396 
4397  cubeGrids.Add(cubeGrid);
4398  }
4399  }
4400  if (!MySandboxGame.IsDedicated)
4401  {
4402  MyHud.PushRotatingWheelVisible();
4403  }
4404  MyMultiplayer.RaiseStaticEvent(s => MyCubeGrid.TryPasteGrid_Implementation, cubeGrids, false, ownerId, Vector3.Zero, false, true);
4405  }
